## How does the internet works

Internet is the ability to connect multipe devices through a network

This is part of networking

Your Device IP -> ISP -> DNS -> Internet -> Connect to Website

use [NsLookup](NsLookup.io) to look up DNS records of a website.

![Diagram](image.png)

You can either buy domains from godaddy or any other provider. 
